  "Say": {
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Hayato, you seem to have adjusted to your new surroundings, though you look more spindly than usual. Do not neglect your training. Nobunaga will not be a pushover."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "Challenging the Oda clan head-on with our army would be suicide. Nobunaga has shown an impressive knowledge of this world in his short time here. It would be like facing a day of sport with improper diet."
      },
      "2": {
        "_dirType": "string",
        "_value": "So, I have something to ask of you. Leave us. Go, and take in this new world. Find allies, find power. Find out what they eat to stay trim... everything is pigs and fat here. Only then will you truly be of any use in the coming battle."
      },
