          "_value": "Yes! You'll find a town with inhabitants to the south of Momijigahara. The enemy has most likely created a pathway to get to it."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirType": "string",
          "_value": "Let me know when you're prepared to depart. And do not tell the others. They will not understand."
